Lukkin is a social network for Social Good

18.description:
Lukkin is the social network where individuals, companies and organizations come together to create Social Good.

They believe social networks can be used for more than just having fun - once they are connected and together, they can also make change in the world.

They created Lukkin to be a space to connect people around common causes. They’ve built a set of tools just for this purpose. Their platform can empower people in working together to improve the problems that the world faces. From visualization and tracking services, to tools to resources for organizing grant data, we will help people create and share the impact they make - in a transparent way.

They don’t believe that a “like” can save a life, or that following a cause on social media alone will change the world. But they do believe in the power of people. And their ability to create things. They believe in the power of collaboration.

Come participate by telling your stories, inspiring your community, and challenging each other to take meaningful action. Together, They can build the world that they want.

Lukkin, a Social Network for Social Good.
